gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df064a4718387800366454a6a253ce34ac8ad661","tid":1476793,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d7439b595525447c98b9c232e7bbea5f2fc3066","tid":1476793,"uid":271676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"動物撚本黎想去但卻步<br />\n<br />\n我都見到你講既野<br />\n但佢地有出post講明撐五大訴求<br />\n如果真係對家應該唔敢講明？<br />\n<br />\n屌我都好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔想仲有貓狗食彈 我好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:25:25.000Z","msg":"咁就要憑自己對眼去睇清楚個集會係做乜<br />\n睇返個集會搞手既fb ，相信你都會搵到真相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/f0WQd7h.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0WQd7h.gif&h=8b9fb401&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05fc526d5de39f0bfddb85e78f7d9edbd9058e70","tid":1476793,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:33:54.000Z","msg":"中"},{"pid":"870cdf5ad978e8f263c37989bb04cfc1aa01fa00","tid":1476793,"uid":120057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d7439b595525447c98b9c232e7bbea5f2fc3066","tid":1476793,"uid":271676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"動物撚本黎想去但卻步<br />\n<br />\n我都見到你講既野<br />\n但佢地有出post講明撐五大訴求<br />\n如果真係對家應該唔敢講明？<br />\n<br />\n屌我都好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔想仲有貓狗食彈 我好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:26:28.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢覺得出好過唔出<br />\n最多有咩唔對路再應變"},{"pid":"64a1420a4f7946c463462c4e840b09ccab5cb28f","tid":1476793,"uid":271676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:51:29.000Z","msg":"我再推！"},{"pid":"05663a032d20afacecde0c36860c0bd3908f9e28","tid":1476793,"uid":280712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d82d3299c13c49d23687bb7f98ceb9a9ae916be","tid":1476793,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:44:59.000Z","msg":"幫我廣傳!!個Page成萬幾人睇，有血性有人性有良知既都同我Share!!! <br />\n<br />\nAnimalSaverHK為何一意孤行?<br />\n<br />\n正仆街，佢地岩岩又發傳媒邀請。重點是有眼球受傷少女既同工出席，仲講明有傳媒訪問時間，咁即係到時一定有行家追問眼球受傷少女既野啦。<br />\n<br />\n我好撚簡單，要講就由佢屋企人或者佢自己出黎講，因之前江湖一直有保密令。究竟呢班閪人想點撚樣呀，動保定抽水呀!!!!<br />\n<br />\n個活動已被大量黃絲及動保界人士及團體杯葛，但仲係要一意孤行去舉行，原來就是因為想爆811少女既身份? <br />\n<br />\n我聽朝就飛，仲要個幾月前就訂好哂，算佢地好彩我去唔到，否則我一定會在記者環節不斷追問佢地過去幾年同建制既關係、同毛守K既關係、同元朗鄉紳既關係、同元朗非法養殖場既關係。但我好肯定，唔止我一個人咁憤怒，而且佢地唔係記者，會用唔係記者既方法去對付佢地。<br />\n<br />\n文:白影"},{"pid":"7e9a0b3838a538844d5cc063a12170438aa36c4c","tid":1476793,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"post去動物group！今次提催淚煙殺狗唔提黃藍"},{"pid":"506229248c7f5a374f57e804336b7475c02eedd4","tid":1476793,"uid":133534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:52:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad9862938b7051c4002ade1ecdee8d16d7e6386f","tid":1476793,"uid":262527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}